{"tid":331242,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果甩頭髮而髮根仲有白色粒粒","createTime":"2017-07-22T03:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T14:40:03.000Z","uid":88183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77b54bb4a6c97f120957dac649c70487f3ed8b93","tid":331242,"uid":88183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:44:07.000Z","msg":"呢幾年開始m字額但明明仲係廿歲頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁上網查下應該係脂溢性脫髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁症狀大約有<br />\n<br />\n1.頭髮油性大、皮脂分泌特別多，即使經常洗頭也難以改變。頭髮一般細軟，並有可能出現枯黃、易斷的症狀。<br />\n2.頭髮脫落從前額(或者前額兩側)和頭頂開始，一般都是慢性掉落，漸漸的頭皮變得清晰可見，但是後腦和兩側的頭髮卻幾乎沒有什麼變化。<br />\n3.髮根有油脂粒<br />\n<br />\n而原因主要係在於皮脂分泌過旺，皮膚中有些成份如油酸、亞油酸、角鯊烯等過量時對毛囊有毒性作用，導致毛皮中毒、枯萎、脫落。<br />\n<br />\n脂溢性脫髮分兩類：急性脂溢性脫髮和慢性脂溢性脫髮。急性脂溢性脫髮症狀是：頭皮油質增多、癢，有頭屑或丘疹，毛髮在短時間內成撮脫落甚至全部脫光，頭皮可有小丘疹，多發生在青春期，以男性較多見，治癒後易復發。慢性脂溢性脫髮症狀是：頭皮油膩發亮，呈塗油狀，有大量灰白色糠皮狀頭屑，頭髮乾燥，缺乏光澤，瘙癢較重，男性頭髮從前額兩側及頭頂部慢慢脫落，幾年或十幾年後形成禿頂<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://read01.com/oxAmOe.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fread01.com%2FoxAmOe.html&d=%2Ftg94tjo1WDcL9EzSfBCB49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=29b4460c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://read01.com/oxAmOe.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/oxxl8m.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fzh-hk%2Fhealth%2Foxxl8m.html&d=%2Ftg94tjo1WDcL9EzSfBCB49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=0e1aed7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/zh-hk/health/oxxl8m.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/health/nx4b4yq.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhealth%2Fnx4b4yq.html&d=%2Ftg94tjo1WDcL9EzSfBCB49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=c2314d4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/health/nx4b4yq.html</a><br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n近年成日係頭頂都有油脂粒，同埋甩既頭髮髮根多數都有油脂粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人有同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左良好生活習慣外仲有無咩洗頭水/醫生介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad7fc71b6af8ab1cc47302f18fc1106d1cb658b","tid":331242,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T03:46:17.000Z","msg":"Search elon musk hair loss<br />\n儲定五十萬"},{"pid":"0944084ceb8b3c82220638c3316a73299590ab23","tid":331242,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:22:20.000Z","msg":"冇計<br />\n<br />\n我係"},{"pid":"ea22a5c78f9a9225f1a3a7882304c426140404d0","tid":331242,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T14:40:03.000Z","msg":"咁同雄禿有咩分別"}]}